name: Adelia ti
description:
Adelia is the nom de plume of a Ukrainian glamor model, now retired. She's real pretty.

I don't drink coffee, so give your money to someone who does. Or keep it. Just gimme them gold stars!

(If you roll high on your Perception, you might notice that I misspelled her name when I did the sample images. I noticed and changed the spelling before I published; Adelia is the correct name.)
